headline.print_headline: Cochran Says He Doesn't Know Much About Tea Party
headline.main: Cochran Says He Doesn't Know Much About Tea Party

lead_paragraph: Veteran Republican Sen. Thad Cochran of Mississippi says he's not familiar with the tea party, even though he's being challenged by a supporter of the populist movement.
